---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Story | Runaway Train Café">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/2698530_orig.jpg');">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-train-brown/70"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-train-cream mb-4">
        Our Story
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-train-cream/90">
        Serving Brownwood in an authentic train car since day one.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Story Content -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-train-cream">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-train-brown leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Runaway Train Café is the most popular and unique café to eat in Brownwood. As soon as you 
          walk in, you feel what it was like to dine in an authentic dining train car with all of its 
          originality. You are always greeted by our friendly staff to take a seat in one of their 
          booths or on a stool at the old-fashioned ice cream counter.
        </p>
        
        <div class="my-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <img 
            src="/9548696_orig.jpg" 
            alt="Interior of Runaway Train Café" 
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full"
          />
          <img 
            src="/884524_orig.jpg" 
            alt="Authentic train car details" 
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-train-brown mt-12 mb-6">The Best Burgers in Town</h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-train-brown/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          All our burgers are fresh half-pound burgers that you can order with or without cheese. 
          Customer favorites include the bacon cheeseburger with jalapeño bacon and the mushroom 
          & Swiss burger. All our burgers are served with either delicious French fries or tots. 
          Also be sure to try beef hot dogs or the kraut.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-train-red font-semibold italic my-8">
          "We have the best burgers you'll ever taste!"
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-train-brown mt-12 mb-6">More Than Burgers</h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-train-brown/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We also serve amazing sandwiches and homemade soup. For the best of both worlds, definitely 
          get the bowl of soup and half sandwich deal! Tasty appetizers and crisp salads are also available.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-train-brown/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          After your mouth watering meal, don't forget to try a single or double scoop of homemade 
          Blue Bell ice cream!
        </p>
        
        <div class="my-12">
          <img 
            src="/219173_orig.jpg" 
            alt="Delicious food at Runaway Train Café" 
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-train-brown mt-12 mb-6">Visit Us Today</h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-train-brown/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Whether you're a Brownwood local or just passing through, make sure to stop by the Runaway 
          Train Café for a meal you won't forget. Our friendly staff and unique atmosphere make every 
          visit special.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12 bg-train-brown text-train-cream rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Come See Us!</h3>
        <p class="text-lg opacity-90 mb-6">
          3600 Stephen F. Austin Dr, Brownwood, TX 76801
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="tel:+13256463333" 
            class="bg-train-red hover:bg-red-800 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z" />
            </svg>
            Call (325) 646-3333
          </a>
          <a 
            href="https://maps.google.com/?q=3600+Stephen+F+Austin+Dr+Brownwood+TX+76801" 
            target="_blank"
            class="bg-train-gold hover:bg-yellow-600 text-train-brown px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Get Directions
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
